title: La Grande Orange - Airport
typeOfFood: American, Pizza, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Outlet at the PHX Sky Harbor Airport, pass security. Has lots of labeled veggie choices (green leaf for vegetarian; orange leaf for vegan). Try the spicy chickpea lettuce wraps or the vegan English muffins.
streetAddress: 3400 E Sky Harbor Blvd, Terminal 4 - D gates
